Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,692)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有沙有海的风水宝地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a luxurious oasis of sand and sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.07,0:01:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoot, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你穿衬衫打领带还怎么游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how can we go swimming when you're in a shirt and tie?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, how foolish of me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听你的马上整改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to remedy said situation right now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就到这间更衣篷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will just use this changing tent here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去换泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to change into my bathing suit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.67,0:01:25.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会偷偷摸摸做别的勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:25.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I won't do anything else
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.67,0:01:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝表现得大惊小怪得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's acting jumpier
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a rattlesnake in a pickle barrel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.30,0:01:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服换归换
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be changing all right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但不换泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not into a bathing suit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着让珊迪瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait until Sandy sees
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带来了空手道装备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I brought my karate gear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪这回肯定打败不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy won't beat me this time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.60,0:01:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我坐拥必胜的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I've got the element on my side
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出其不意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The element of surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I most certainly am ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备嗨起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to get it on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也带来了空手道装备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we both brought our karate gear
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来英雄所见略同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great minds think alike, I suppose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能是倒下了  但我还没放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may be down, but I'm not out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way to go, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个土豆沙拉三天才做好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It took us three days to make that potato salad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.72,0:02:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是珊迪没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Sandy all right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在沙底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm very sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她叫珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's "Sandy"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她名字跟沙底谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's her name and she's also covered in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:51.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,804)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在德克萨斯老家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back in Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都管冰淇淋叫冻牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we call ice cream "frozen cow juice"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a sec
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁朝我扔纸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who threw that piece of paper at me?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家排队干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's everyone waiting in line for?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.25,0:03:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美女  这是进强人俱乐部的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, fair lass, it be the line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get into the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:18.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,258)}强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.63,0:03:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七大洋有史以来最强人的水手俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the roughest, toughest, sailor club
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever to be built under the seven seas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有最坏的恶霸才进得去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the baddest of the bad can get in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得有肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to have muscles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肌肉上也得有肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to have muscles on your muscles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼球上也得有肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to have muscles on your eyeballs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来可以进去玩个尽兴了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like a rip-snortin' good time, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  咱们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough are ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早餐吃了一碗钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had a bowl of nails for breakfast this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没配牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without any milk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1030,904)}妈
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough are ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,730)}哇
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有没有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got any more tattoos?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya inside, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough are ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tough am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有新买的未开封番茄酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a new bottle of ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.92,0:04:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能用热水冲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I could just run this under some hot water
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方对你来说太强了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is too tough for you, little man
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对我来说太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too tough for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点道理也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's downright ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.68,0:04:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上周我给香料园胶水  踢到脚趾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stubbed my toe last week
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while watering my spice garden
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只哭了二十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I only cried for 20 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到那边应该舒服点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'd be more comfortable over at that place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,304)}儿童乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿童乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Hut Jr's?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我只能去儿童乐园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I belong at Weenie Hut Jr's?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我其实是在指隔壁那家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was actually pointing to the place next to it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(502,230)}婴儿宝宝乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,婴儿宝宝乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super Weenie Hut Jr's?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非你觉得自己够强  能打败我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless you think you're tough enough to fight me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(574,260)}儿童乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的收藏进度如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's your collection coming along?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我故意吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well I don't mean to brag
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进度可乐观了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's pretty sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要入手第347册
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the process of acquiring issue 347
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就能集齐第四套了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which will give me my fourth complete set
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一群小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What weenies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想再来一杯加柠檬皮的无糖可乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care for another diet cola with a lemon twist
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不是小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的传感器显示  你就是小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my sensors indicate that you are indeed a weenie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742,856)}是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内心是隐藏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't hide what's inside
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要求进入你们的俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I demand entrance into your club
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,理由是  我不是小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the grounds that I am not a weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷吉  怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reg, how's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚说到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你叫雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, your name's Reg?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能给我走开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you get outta here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mark my words, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定进得去强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will get into the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进不去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Couldn't get in, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要的正是强人的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you need is a tough hairdo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强人俱乐部得有强人的发型才能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one gets into the double-S without a tough hairdo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I disagree
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到有个秃头进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw a guy going in there and he was bald
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我见过那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他那不算秃头  是剃了光头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wasn't bald, he had a shaved head
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剃光头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shaved
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也算发型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a hairdo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Case closed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.50,0:06:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想他说要去假发店什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe he said something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about going to the wig store
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check and mate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近来可好  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's shaking, my man?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not much
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前有见过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, haven't I seen you before?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不见得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doubt it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我漂泊在外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a drifter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好漂来这座小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just blew into town
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你家俱乐部挺强人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heard your club was pretty tough
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想过来瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好  有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey everybody, what's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.11,0:07:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can go in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请让我进去你们的俱乐部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to gain entrance to your social club, please
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的发型肯定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe my hairdo is in order
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你支持秃头派还是剃头派
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So where do you stand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the whole bald vs. shaved debate?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey-ya, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来了才热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now it's a party
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  你新纹了身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, check out the new ink
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我拿它变花样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what I can make it do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个能变什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about that one?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说我不记得纹过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't remember getting this one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能让它跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you make it dance?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.10,0:07:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想进去  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, little man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚排在你前面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was in front of you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you weren't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我骗你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you callin' me a liar?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't callin' you for dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个都很强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're both plenty tough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也跟着一起打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was in that scrap
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到你逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw you running
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你真打再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you get in a real fight, then we'll talk
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是时候要更上一层楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess it's time to take it up a notch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要再来一份圣代吗  小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care for another sundae, weenie?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not a weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急  大家都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Relax, you're among friends
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.12,0:08:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友才不来儿童乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My friends don't hang out at Weenie Hut Jr's
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒是  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You tell 'em, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我双童周三都会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm always here on Double-Weenie Wednesday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实双童周三现在变周五了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, they moved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double-Weenie Wednesday to Friday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且今天是周一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, today's Monday
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来今天是超童周一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's Mega-Weenie Monday?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在那是周天的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's now on Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,婴儿宝宝乐园有超童周一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super Weenie Hut Jr's has a Mega-Weenie Monday
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你那是怪童周一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're thinking of Monster-Weenie Monday
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没空争这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去跟不熟的肌肉男找茬打架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go pick a fight with a muscular stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这样才能进强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the only way of getting into the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob, you can't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没得选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a suggestion
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就假打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not fake a fight?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个办法好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a bad idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以拿外号骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can call me a couple of bad names
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就打起来  然后就能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we rumble, next thing you know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺理成章让你进强人俱乐部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're in the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像也没多大代价
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I've got nothing to lose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么就没法帮我们解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How come you never help us with our problems?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是机器人  不会专门制造奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a robot, not a miracle worker
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午安  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Afternoon, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, little man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是不能进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still can't go in
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.20,0:09:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那真是气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes me pretty mad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去打个谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might have to beat someone up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能浇灭心中的无名业火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to get rid of all this blind fury
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为不顺眼的那位深表遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel pretty sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the next guy who looks at me funny
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about that guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't be silly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他又没惹到谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's not bothering anybody
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, not like
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光站着嬉皮笑脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Standing there all smiling and whatnot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得多学学礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody ought to teach you some manners
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  可我得警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, but I must warn you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚好是世界冠军级
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I happen to be a world championship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,678)}搏击选手
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搏击选手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"kick box er"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你是不是戴维琼斯的魔种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're the demon seed of Davey Jones
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都得下地狱去  胖墩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going down, Tubby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胖墩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tubby?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准叫我胖墩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody calls me Tubby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要让我赢的  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to let me win, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  求你饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please, have mercy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你连碰都没碰就把他打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You destroyed that guy without even touching him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没想过我会这么说  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd say this, but
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go ahead in
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can go in?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  没想到这一刻会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, I never thought this moment would come
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经够强  可以进强人俱乐部了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,am tough enough to get into the Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我一生中最快乐的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the happiest day of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.02,0:11:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你冲进门  踩到冰块滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ran inside and slipped on an ice cube
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,934)}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,540)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我踩到冰块滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I slipped on an ice cube
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身上都是伤  害我好痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and got covered in boo-boos
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痛痛是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo-boos, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该去那家医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you guys want that hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,488)}儿童综合医院
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿童综合医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Hut General?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.51,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(405,397)\pos(730,540)}章鱼威廉回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:25.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz25.1\pos(325.802,486)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(327.802,482)\frz25.42}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(421.802,346)\frz24.04}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(317.802,350)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(467.802,672)\frz21.55}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,474)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seven
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.37,0:12:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,six
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,five
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,four
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.05,0:12:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.96,0:12:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不干了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm done with my shift, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,容我发言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And let me just say
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终有一天会功成名就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there will come a day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I will make something of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.95,0:12:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不用踏进这家小破店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I will never have to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,set foot in this grease trap again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午休之后再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll see you after your lunch break, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就坐我的私人快艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I just took my private yacht
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,渡过了我的私人大湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,across my private lake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抵达了我的私人机场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my private heliport
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的私人小岛只能坐飞机离开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the only way off my private island
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我高中的死对头  章鱼威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my arch rival from high school, Squilliam Fancyson
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让他看到我穿着蟹堡王的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't let him see me in my Krusty Krab uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在午休吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your lunch break, eh, Squiddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.97,0:13:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.21,0:13:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你近来可好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha been up to?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你失败的事情我全在成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just succeeding in everything you've failed in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也没多了不起嘛  章鱼威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are no great shakes, Squilliam Fancyson
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都能在裤头村这种穷乡僻壤发迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone can be a big shot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a hick town like Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.08,0:13:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就说说你高中毕业以来有何高就吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hear what you've accomplished
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since high school, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别怕  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be intimidated, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象他只穿内裤的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try to imagine him in his underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  他身材真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, he's hot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从事的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm, uh, in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐饮行业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,food service
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  你该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在当收银员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a cashier
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't lie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说谎更容易完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lying always makes it worse
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我坐拥一家五星级餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I own a five-star restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我都不知道你会这么成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I had no idea you were such a success
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.80,0:14:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让我来参观你餐厅  我将不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I would be honored
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you would allow me to come to your restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,T-t-t-t-t-t-tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, we'll all come
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My treat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等他们今晚来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When they get here tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定都看得出来我是大骗子加大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'll see I'm just a big phony and a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo-hoo
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用世界最小的小提琴为你奏悲歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me play a sad song for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the world's smallest violin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is serious
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这真的是全世界最小的小提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this really is the world's smallest violin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你让我经营一下餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let me run the restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一晚就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for just one night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的需要让章鱼威廉大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really need to impress Squilliam
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章章章  章鱼威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sq-Sq-Sq-Squilliam?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活在你的梦想里还赚了好几百万那位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who made millions doing what you wish you could do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.85,0:14:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别往伤口撒盐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't rub it in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这就打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take him to the cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉再二十分钟就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Men, Squilliam Fancyson will be here in 20 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  我们要把蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we need to turn the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.25,0:15:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽快变成高档餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a fancy restaurant as soon as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,军团可以让我生活更美好  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought the Corps would straighten out my life, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,军团
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Corps?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这又不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick this isn't the
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没得选了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beggars can't be choosers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会端庄大方地拿客人帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you take hats
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a dignified and sophisticated manner?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要像娘娘腔那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like a weenie?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子给我好吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your hat, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子给我好吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your hat, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  我听够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I've heard enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任务交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got the job
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你先前在美食号服务过是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, didn't you once serve on the S.S. Gourmet?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让你当大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be our chef
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm saying this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来担任服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to have to be the waiter
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得负责走到桌前接单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the guy who goes to tables and takes orders
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他餐厅是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do other restaurants do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, they do that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  章鱼威廉已经上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen, Squilliam is on his way
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只剩二十分钟不到的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you have less than 20 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速成高档餐厅服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to become a fancy waiter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你就看这本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so read this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十分钟不到速成高档餐厅服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"How To Become a Fancy Waiter in Less Than 20 Minutes"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会记下每一页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll memorize every page
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个标点符号都不落下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right down to the punctuation mark
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  职位都安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I've got all the positions filled
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计能成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just might pull this off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说了快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底交不交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you going to hand it over or not?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许给我顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you back-sass me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不过就保管个帽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just the hat-check guy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.12,0:16:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没多大必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing essential
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,670)}豆
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,传统古法制作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Made 'em the old-fashioned way
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  把那玩意给我扔出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you got to take them out of the
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷  这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy fish paste, what is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是开胃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the appetizer
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, I thought you said
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是美食号上的主厨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you were the head chef on the S.S. Gourmet?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有  我在美食号是扫厕所的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I cleaned the bathrooms on the Gourmet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是拉肚子号的主厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was the head chef on the S.S. Diarrhea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  一定要救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you got to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星跟蟹老板不靠谱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and Mr. Krabs aren't working out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼威廉就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squilliam's almost here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, and
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每句  每段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every sentence, every paragraph
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.47,0:17:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spoons
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.97,0:17:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bread
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.35,0:17:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pepper
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑子快塞爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brain is full to bursting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再让我记客人点的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I have to memorize a single order
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就真要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to explode
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  先撑着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来放松个一秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just take a second here to relax
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再放松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little more
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再放松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little more
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你脑袋放空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to empty your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.27,0:17:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放空我脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Empty my mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放空你脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Empty your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放空我脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Empty my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抛开心中一切杂念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Empty your mind of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘掉跟高级餐饮服务无关的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that doesn't have to do with fine dining
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只记得高级餐饮服务  还有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine dining and breathing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到老大的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just got an order from the boss
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把跟高级餐饮服务无关的一切全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dump everything that isn't about fine dining
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quicker, quicker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,352)}捉水母
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始扔掉开始扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start dumping, start dumping
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:09.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,352)}童年回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,386)}香料种植\N小窍门
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  加快动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get moving
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.86,0:18:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我付你工资是叫你来干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I paying you for?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又没付我工资
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't pay me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't even exist
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就只是个具象化的精巧比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just a clever visual metaphor
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把抽象的思想概念拟人化了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,used to personify the abstract concept of thought
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再插科打诨就别干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more crack like that and you're out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家有三个小孩要养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have three kids
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:29.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,786)}数学
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't working
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去找章鱼威廉多争取点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta go tell Squilliam I need more time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要去找章鱼威廉跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just go to Squilliam and tell him and
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squilliam, you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱都准备好被你的五星级餐厅迷倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all ready to be dazzled
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by your five-star restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.93,0:18:59.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  章鱼威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:18:59.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Squilliam
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得向你解释
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to explain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,解释什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Explain what?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That you, Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.06,0:19:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高中公认最容易班门弄斧的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,voted most likely to suck eggs in high school
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把一个破烂汉堡摊子办成五星级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are trying to pass off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a lousy burger stand as a five-star
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.76,0:19:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊这啊这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hommina, hommina
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊这要来就餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Table for Hommina?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我立刻让你们就座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can seat you immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you do all this?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was easy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放空脑袋就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,once I cleared my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹老板跟派大星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about Krabs and Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妥善安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taken care of
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, please
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为您推荐今晚菜单中的蟹黄新堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From our menu tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,might I recommend the Krabby Newburg?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(826,722)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选用最优质的陈年进口海草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We take the finest cuts of aged, imported kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以园中的药草加以填充
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stuff them with herbs from our garden
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用羊皮纸包好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wrap them in parchment
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配上斩获过大奖的香葱橄榄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with our award-winning shallot tapenade
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.57,0:20:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于柴火陶制烤炉中慢烤六小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slow-roast them for six hours
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in our wood-fired, clay-filled oven, or kiva
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再用稍煮的珊瑚点缀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and serve them with a garnish of wilted coral
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放上红木板为你献上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a mahogany plank
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是妙极了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掐我一把  我一定是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinch me, I must be dreaming
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果还有需要  随时叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you need anything else, just call
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  真谢谢你所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I can't thank you enough for all you're doing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只会高级餐饮服务和呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine dining and breathing are all I know how to do
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.55,0:20:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉真以为我坐拥五星级餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squilliam thinks I own a five-star restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来火上浇油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to rub it in his face
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉  我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squilliam, I'm waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都堪称一绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything is fabulous
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物  气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The food, the atmosphere
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's flawless
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的话  请你念下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case, I need you to read this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Squidward Tentacles"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I need you to wear this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,754)}章鱼哥第一
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥坐拥全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Squidward Tentacles has the fanciest"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  再念一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, one more time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.47,0:20:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥坐拥全裤头村最高档的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has the fanciest restaurant in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且他没有班门弄斧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he does not suck eggs"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I must tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.15,0:21:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.71,0:21:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正让我折服的是你的优秀服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What really won me over was your brilliant waiter
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.17,0:21:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's as if
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只会高级餐饮服务和呼吸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all he knows is fine dining and breathing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must know your name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, your name, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惠灵顿牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beef Wellington?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, your name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叉子放左边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fork on the left?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop joking
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名字告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him your name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got nothing on a name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on baby, what's the name?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把他名字扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We threw out his name
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so very sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是中了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what has gotten into that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胳肢窝要再来点汤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More soup for your armpits?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the food
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面还要再加点奶酪吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like some cheese on that, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快逃  开胃菜来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives, everyone, it's the appetizer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,740)}章鱼哥  收银员
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squiddy, I'm waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.00,0:22:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a fraud
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.47,0:22:42.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞了这可悲徒劳的一出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:42.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was all a futile, pathetic attempt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想让你大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to impress you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这并不是我的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't really my restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.96,0:22:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是个收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just a cashier
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.43,0:22:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I understand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也有话想跟你坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a confession to make myself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.51,0:22:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的大好生活都是瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made everything up about my life
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没快艇  喷气机什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no yachts, jets or anything
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.65,0:23:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想让你大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to impress you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糟糕可悲的事实就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horrible, sad truth is
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是个收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a cashier, too
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.72,0:23:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.97,0:23:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我富得流油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm filthy, stinking rich
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.50,0:23:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来坐坐我的热气球赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's all take a ride in my balloon/casino
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.42,0:23:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.19,0:23:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我头好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got such a headache
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.93,0:23:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The usual
Dialogue: 1,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you get out of here
